deck_description:
The main goal is to keep a large amount of cards in your hand. Go for tiger then wolf, or lots of sabre tooths. Use the bear and wings play for draw power. Various edge imps allow for more card advantage whilst being used for fusions. This deck is purely OTK based so there is no traps, but this deck a can still work after the first turn. This deck is suprisingly resiliant to solemns but an anti spell fragrence on dimentional barrier will smash this deck.

